title: Open Concept - Two Bedroom, One Bath
posting_body: ['Living space:', 'Spacious with Laminate dark hardwood floors.', 'Recess lighting with updated LED Fixtures for energy conserving.', 'Dining Room: Great space with a window that lets in lots of light.', 'Kitchen: Caesar stone counters (White), and lots of cabinetry with self-closing mechanisms.', 'Stainless steel appliances.', 'Dishwasher included!', 'Bathroom: Craftsman tile work throughout.', 'Very Bright space.', 'Heater and motion sensor fan.', 'Bedrooms: Low profile carpet, with abundant closet space.', 'Laundry Room: Compact stackable Washer and Dryer.', 'Location Offers:', 'Paved trail Across Lake Washington', 'Park Directly behind our building', 'Close to five nearby parks for sports tennis & basketball courts, dog park, water park', "Close to Seattle's downtown stores and nightlife", 'One mile from downtown and hospitals Swedish, Providence, Virginia Mason, Harborview', 'Bike Path To Sound Trail: Ride to Seattle, Bellevue or Mercer Island Close to Seahawks and Mariner Games', 'Bus Lines: 14 off of Jackson and 23rd- International district, downtown.', '27 off Yesler and 22nd- Downtown, First Hill, Capitol Hill, University District', 'Easy access to I-5 and I-90.']
